DocTracker: Student Document Management System
A professional Django-based portal for study-abroad consultancies to manage, track, and verify student documents efficiently.
ğŸš€ Key Features
 * Counselor Dashboard: Centralized view of all students with real-time progress tracking.
 * Secure Student Portal: Password-less, token-based (UUID) access for secure file uploads.
 * Dynamic Workflows: Automatic status updates from 'Pending' to 'Uploaded'.
 * Review System: Counselors can verify or reject documents with direct feedback notes.
 * Responsive Design: Built with Tailwind CSS for mobile and desktop compatibility.
